data.name: insTb1.ToolTip
data.value: Position(s) to insert text at in integers. You may use spaces, commas, forward slashes, or pipes to separate, for example: 16 32 16,32 16/32 16|32 You don't have to stay consistent, you could type "16|32/64" and it would still work, separating them into 16, 32, and 64.
